        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Junk golems are constructed using random metal and electronic scrap found in junkyards, such as rusted pieces of vehicles, broken vidscreens, and discarded food tins. They\u2019re favored by certain tribes of space goblins, who find their ingenuity in building these hulking constructs matched only by their prudence in making a hasty retreat when the golem inevitably goes berserk."
        }
